'''公共事務黨'''（{{lang-cs|Věci veřejné}}，缩写为VV）是[[捷克|捷克]]的一个已不存在的[[保守自由主義|保守自由主義]]政黨。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Deal struck on Czech government |first=Andrew |last=Gardner |newspaper=[[歐洲之聲|歐洲之聲]] |date=30 June 2010 |url=http://www.europeanvoice.com/article/2010/06/deal-struck-on-czech-government/68368.aspx |accessdate= |archive-date=2012-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314004735/http://www.europeanvoice.com/article/2010/06/deal-struck-on-czech-government/68368.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Czech female MPs have reduced politics by posing as pin-ups |first=Peggy |last=Watson |newspaper=[[衛報|衛報]] |date=2 September 2010 |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2010/sep/02/czech-calendar-pin-up-female-mps |accessdate= |archive-date=2012-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007063644/http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2010/sep/02/czech-calendar-pin-up-female-mps |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ihsglobalinsight.com/SDA/SDADetail18952.htm |title=Election 2010: New Czech Centre-Right Government Assumes Power, Eyes Reforms |author=|date=14 July 2010 |work=|publisher=[[Global_Insight|Global Insight]] |accessdate=3 December 2010}}</ref> 领袖為反建制[[調查報導|調查記者]]與作家[[拉代克·約恩|拉代克·約恩]]（Radek John）<ref name="Public Affairs party remains a">{{Cite news |title=Public Affairs party remains a mystery to many |first=Ruth |last=Fraňková |newspaper=[[Radio_Prague|Radio Prague]] |date=31 May 2010 |url=http://www.radio.cz/en/article/128482 |accessdate=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2010-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100604072102/http://www.radio.cz/en/article/128482 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其主要綱領為政治透明與反貪腐。該黨目前在[[捷克眾議院|捷克眾議院]]擁有24席。

除了反貪腐，公共事務黨還支持[[財政保守主義|財政保守主義]]。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Centre-right wins Czech election on austerity plan |first=Robert |last=Mueller |coauthors=Mlcochova, Jana |agency=Reuters |date=29 May 2010 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE64S0N820100529 |accessdate=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2010-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100601070908/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE64S0N820100529 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 該黨有部分[[右派民粹主義|右派民粹主義]]政策<ref>{{de icon}} {{Cite news |title=Tschechien: Jugend vereint gegen Linksparteien |first=Alexandra |last=Klausmann |newspaper=[[Wiener_Zeitung|Wiener Zeitung]] |date=21 May 2010 |url=http://www.wienerzeitung.at/default.aspx?tabID=3861&alias=wzo&cob=494591 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606122248/http://www.wienerzeitung.at/default.aspx?tabID=3861&alias=wzo&cob=494591 |archivedate=2011年6月6日 |accessdate=2011年7月23日 }}</ref>，不反對移民<ref name="Public Affairs party remains a" />，但有少部分黨員的立場更接近[[中間偏左|中間偏左]]。<ref>{{Cite news |title=Snap Analysis: Czech vote good for markets but new party a risk |first=Jan |last=Lopatka |agency=Reuters |date=29 May 2010 |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE64S1WX20100529 |accessdate=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2010-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100603065553/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE64S1WX20100529 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 該黨支持[[直接民主制|直接民主制]]，黨員可透過網路公投改變政黨路線。

==歷史==
公共事務黨成立於2001年，大部分時間都專心於[[布拉格|布拉格]]的地方政治，特別是在[[布拉格第一區|布拉格第一區]]。<ref name="Prague politics player Public Affairs">{{Cite news |title=Prague politics player Public Affairs enters lower house |first= |last= |newspaper=[[Czech_News_Agency|Czech News Agency]] |date=29 May 2010 |url=http://praguemonitor.com/2010/05/31/prague-politics-player-public-affairs-enters-lower-house }}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Czech parties hold coalition talks |first= |last= |newspaper=[[Aljazeera|Aljazeera]] |date=31 May 2010 |url=http://english.aljazeera.net/news/europe/2010/05/2010531155019929513.html |accessdate=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2011-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110209223414/http://english.aljazeera.net/news/europe/2010/05/2010531155019929513.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2009年6月，拉代克·約恩成為黨魁<ref name="Prague politics player Public Affairs" />，之後該黨成為[[2010年捷克大選|2010年捷克大選]]的競爭者之一，民調顯示公共事務黨已跨越5%門檻，有時還超越[[基督教民主聯盟-捷克斯洛伐克人民黨|基督教民主聯盟-捷克斯洛伐克人民黨]]與[[綠黨_(捷克)|綠黨]]。約恩與[[卡雷爾·施瓦岑貝格|卡雷爾·施瓦岑貝格]]成為捷克最受歡迎的政治人物。<ref>{{Cite news |title=A song by Marta |first= |last= |newspaper=[[The_Economist|The Economist]] |date=20 May 2010 |url=http://www.economist.com/world/europe/displaystory.cfm?story_id=16167808 |accessdate=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2010-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100529012621/http://www.economist.com/world/europe/displayStory.cfm?story_id=16167808 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

公共事務黨在本屆大選獲得10.9%的得票率，拿下24席。該黨目前與其他兩個[[中間偏右|中間偏右]]政黨：[[公民民主黨|公民民主黨]]與[[傳統、責任、繁榮黨|傳統、責任、繁榮黨]]組成執政聯盟。

== 爭議 ==
2011年4月，該黨領袖兼交通部長[[維·特巴塔|維·特巴塔]]（Vít Bárta），被指控收取同黨議員Jaroslav Škárka、Stanislav Huml、Kristýna Kočí等人的賄絡。這些議員隨後遭到開除黨籍。這次事件成為執政聯盟內的嚴重問題。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.tyden.cz/rubriky/domaci/koci-vyzvala-bartu-k-rezignaci-huml-vystoupil-z-klubu-john-mluvi-o-provokaci_198529.html?showTab=diskutovane|title=VV vyhnaly Kočí z klubu i ze strany a vyzvaly ji: Vzdej se mandátu|date=7 April 2011|publisher=[[Týden|Týden]]|language=cs|accessdate=8 April 2011|archive-date=2019-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190613065251/https://www.tyden.cz/rubriky/domaci/koci-vyzvala-bartu-k-rezignaci-huml-vystoupil-z-klubu-john-mluvi-o-provokaci_198529.html?showTab=diskutovane|dead-url=no}}</ref>

